    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 engine. This power unit delivers a linear torque curve and an exhilarating 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis architecture is enhanced by Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and precise turn-in. This example maintains excellent mechanical integrity with recent preventative maintenance on rod bearings and throttle actuators. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering a pure analog feel in a modern-classic silhouette.",
