      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, high-quality daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium space; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the heated seats, functions as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently undergone a full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive cooling system inspection. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brake rotors were serviced within the last 5,000 miles. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a documented service history, offering a dependable and sophisticated driving experience for its next owner.",
