    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec icon powered by the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry is maintained with refreshed bushings and upgraded Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While it displays honest cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014specifically compression and rod bearings\u2014remain within optimal tolerances. This is a mechanically sorted, high-performance machine ready for the apex.",
